text.paragraph:
Carefully consider the potential benefits and risks of indomethacin capsules and other treatment options before deciding to use indomethacin capsules. Use the lowest effective dosage for the shortest duration consistent with individual patient treatment goals [ see Warnings and Precautions (
5
)].

As advancing years appear to increase the possibility of adverse reactions, indomethacin should be used with greater care in the elderly. [ see Use in Specific Populations (
8.5
)]

